port lang/luajit
type port
target @any
reason "DragonFly-specific memory allocation adjustments for pre-5.5 compat: MAP_TRYFIXED, rlimit handling, region-start tuning. Upstream 2.1.0.20260304 has restructured lj_alloc.c with probing allocator; most old hunks are obsolete. Retaining only the rlimit hack for DragonFly >= 5.5 if needed."

